            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Albius Le<lb break="no" n="2"/>monia Bon<expan><ex>on</ex><abbr>i</abbr></expan><lb break="no" n="3"/>a an<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>o</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> XL <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>XVII <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Einfache Rechteckstele mit gerahmtem Inschriftfeld, unten abgebrochen. Fundort nach Schnitzler 2010: Route des Romains 6.</p>
            </div>
